    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<strong>Swordmin'z Dream</strong> is a mini-maximalist two-to-four player fighting game focused around quick matches and a volatile neutral space. Built with an emphasis on <strong>fast, high-risk play</strong>, matches can be won or lost with a single well-placed hit, but you can turn the tide quickly with strong parry mechanics.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389140/extras/64162299af612721875574ae9f0d4a2a.avif?t=1721106229\" width=600 height=64 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389140/extras/12c56bb8420076d9a8411f423b7f138e.webp?t=1721106229\" width=596 height=42 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389140/extras/153e7e2075aaa548c906d3f1fe3eb8d9.avif?t=1721106229\" width=600 height=88 /></span><br>A whole cast of strange little characters awaits, each with their own quirks and strategies.<br>Alongside fundamental characters like <strong>SWORDMIN</strong> and <strong>BLADEMIN</strong> you'll meet characters like <strong>VERY STRONGSMIN</strong>, who has a one-hit-kill attack, <strong>SHOOTSMIN</strong>, who just Has A Gun, or <strong>Júlian St. Clair</strong> who cannot attack at all. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389140/extras/f0e46c9024b4fbdfd5f82ab3f37b8ef3.avif?t=1721106229\" width=600 height=76 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389140/extras/777d62778f9d7f908f271c0d45ae5294.webp?t=1721106229\" width=596 height=42 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389140/extras/fddeae452f953da7139473283da312d7.avif?t=1721106229\" width=600 height=89 /></span><br>In your travels you'll span the breadth of <strong>MINTOPIA</strong> and see all the sights it has to offer.<br>From thriving cities to barren wastelands to tropical paradises and mountain peaks, there's always something nice to look at.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389140/extras/3963a07632f37ee2f68a3cd65f709e24.webp?t=1721106229\" width=596 height=42 /></span><br>Nearly every move in the game can be countered with a well-timed parry.<br>Punches, kicks, sword slashes, bullets, balls of concentrated ki, even explosions can be swiftly deflected if your timing is right.<br>If you have the meter for it, you can even parry out of hit stun, for high-stakes reversals.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389140/extras/f122672879ef32949c5787baab4016c0.webp?t=1721106229\" width=596 height=42 /></span><br>Great for parties! Four players can play two simultaneous matches with the winners facing off seamlessly.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389140/extras/75e37da0f630527a69a50cbf1449abc4.webp?t=1721106229\" width=596 height=42 /></span><br>Both two-player and four-player tag-team modes are available for some chaotic fun! <br>Lots of interesting character combinations to play around with.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389140/extras/df8359fc00fcb168356a4d57ed848c95.webp?t=1721106229\" width=596 height=42 /></span><br>Team Battle is also available!! Put your matchup knowledge to the test in 3v3 duels.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389140/extras/1ee8c05e0c4076adf151f9bd09671118.webp?t=1721106229\" width=596 height=42 /></span><br>Movelists are small yet impactful, matches are quick, and characters have clearly defined win conditions.<br>Swordmin'z Dream's <strong>Mini-Maximalist</strong> ethos means each design element is a small idea taken to a logical extreme.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389140/extras/6918832d28f884139bdb9c0b0c84f70e.avif?t=1721106229\" width=600 height=65 /></span>",
